com.chute.sdk.v2.api.album

Class GCAlbums

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chute.sdk.v2.api.album.GCAlbums

  • public class GCAlbums
extends Object
    The GCAlbums class is a helper class that contains methods regarding AlbumModel. The API enables users and developers to access the following methods: creating, deleting, editing albums, getting list and album statistics, getting an asset or a list of assets from a specific album.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  GCAlbums.Assets
      The GCAlbums.Assets class is an inner class which contains methods for getting a specific asset out of an album or a list of assets
